    Verse: 19
Tags:
  - Perfection
---
Behind this world of unreality and seeming imperfection is the Perfect
World of Reality, the perfect expression of the Divine Idea. ... The perfect
man already IS, and as this Truth is revealed so is he brought into
manifestation.
